  "detailed_description": "<h1>Recommended for you</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Light Up The Sky</strong><br><br>As you guide your tiny hero through a visually stunning world, you'll encounter a myriad of obstacles, from treacherous thorns to tricky jumps and cunning predators. But fear not, for you possess the power to outshine them all! Use your ethereal glow to navigate the treacherous terrain and keep your fellow fireflies safe.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/8386c12350dcf9d2c325dd997e8784e4.poster.avif?t=1700509843\" width=600 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/8386c12350dcf9d2c325dd997e8784e4.webm?t=1700509843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/8386c12350dcf9d2c325dd997e8784e4.mp4?t=1700509843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collecting stars isn't just for show – each one you gather brightens the forest even more and brings you one step closer to victory. With each star you collect, the night sky becomes a canvas of beauty and hope.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/f2e88f1548664b876e1596befe72199f.poster.avif?t=1700509843\" width=600 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/f2e88f1548664b876e1596befe72199f.webm?t=1700509843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/f2e88f1548664b876e1596befe72199f.mp4?t=1700509843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>'Light Up the Sky' offers a unique and heartwarming gameplay experience, where your skills and reflexes are put to the test, and your goal is to save a world filled with wonder. Will you be the hero these fireflies need? Get ready to embark on an enchanting journey, as you light up the sky and kindle the flames of hope in the hearts of all who play. Play 'Light Up the Sky' and experience the magic for yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/613296d594ac5900fe6e30400d99c9e3.poster.avif?t=1700509843\" width=600 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/613296d594ac5900fe6e30400d99c9e3.webm?t=1700509843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/613296d594ac5900fe6e30400d99c9e3.mp4?t=1700509843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1700509843\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1700509843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681640/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1700509843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
